investigation.title: CI Asteroid Regolith as an In Situ Plant Growth Medium for Space Crop Production
investigation.description: Human expansion into the solar system is currently at the forefront of space research. For our astronauts to survive, they will need to be fed a healthy and nutritious diet on a consistent basis.
